§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Let $K ⊂ 𝗥^n$ be a proper cone. ⦉

  ‖ Define a relation $≼_K ⊂ 𝗥^n × 𝗥^n$ by $(x, y) ∈ ≼_K$ if
    $y - x ∈ K$. ⦉

  ‖ We call $≼_K$ the ❬cone-ordering❭ (or ❬generalized
    inequality❭) of $K$. ⦉
